      <li><a href="#faze-2" class="toc-link" data-section="faze-2">Fáze 2: První iterace</a></li>
      <li><a href="#faze-3" class="toc-link" data-section="faze-3">Fáze 3: PI Close</a></li>
      <li><a href="#faze-4" class="toc-link" data-section="faze-4">Fáze 4: Kontinuální provoz</a></li>
      <li><a href="#checklist" class="toc-link" data-section="checklist">Checklist</a></li>
      <li><a href="#cli-reference" class="toc-link" data-section="cli-reference">CLI Reference</a></li>
      <li><a href="#architektura" class="toc-link" data-section="architektura">Architektura</a></li>
      <li><a href="#troubleshooting" class="toc-link" data-section="troubleshooting">Troubleshooting</a></li>
